      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, add your<strong> white wine vinegar</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>warm water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to a small bowl and stir together</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>shallot[s] </strong>as thinly as you can, then add them to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
