    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>curry powder</strong> to a medium bowl with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and stir it all together – this is your <strong>marinade</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken breast strips</strong> to the marinade, give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your<strong> marinated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
