      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
