    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> marinated chicken </strong>and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until charred and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>kebab shop-style chicken</strong></p>",
