    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, combine your<strong> mayo</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and<strong> </strong>2 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp] </span>[4 tsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>– this is your <strong>garlic mayo</strong></p>",
