    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are lightly golden, divide them into a pile for per person on the baking tray[s]</p><p>Divide the<strong> grated cheese</strong> between each pile</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 3-4 min or until the cheese is melted and golden – these are your <strong>cheesy chips</strong></p>",
