    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>kebab shop-style chicken </strong>over the <strong>cheesy chips</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong>,<strong> chopped tomato</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p><p>Garnish with a drizzle of <strong>garlic mayo</strong> and <strong>ketchup</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
